com.sun.mail.imap.protocol

Class UIDSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.mail.imap.protocol.UIDSet

  • public class UIDSet
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds the 'start' and 'end' for a range of UIDs. Just like MessageSet except using long instead of int.
